

<div class="banner">
    <div class="innerbanner">
        <img src="~/Content/Images/BannerHeader.png" width="500px" height="250px" />
        <h1> International Haarlem Film Festival's latest news</h1>

        <p>
            Every year the IHFF tries to offer you the best movies considering the desired theme.
            This years theme is 'Science of Fiction'. This webpage will offer you all avaible restaurants and films in Haarlem.
            You can also find multiple cultural events, for the real adventurers.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>
<br />
<div class="homeArticles">
    <article class="articlehome">

        <h3 class="homeart"> Films</h3>
        <img width="182" height="268" src="~/Content/Images/wallepoging2.jpg" id="winkelmandjeimg" />
        <p class="articletekst">
            IHFF provides numerous amounts of movies, all with the mentioned 'Science of Fiction' theme.
            The films will be displayed in a range of Haarlem's finest theaters.
            Make sure to take a look at all available theaters and times, and pick your desired movie!
        </p>
        @Html.ActionLink("Show me films!", "Woensdag", "Film", null, new { @class = "btn btn-addOtherEvent" })

    </article>

    <article class="articlehome">

        <h3 class="homeart"> Food</h3>
        <img width="182" height="268" src="~/Content/Images/Home3.png" id="winkelmandjeimg" />
        <p class="articletekst">
            The region Kennemerland provides numerous high quality restaurants. IHFF has made an selecction of 
            the best price/quality ratio restaurants located in Haarlem and Bloemendaal. IHFF's Food page displays these restaurants
            based on the named locations.  
            
        </p>
        @Html.ActionLink("Show me food!", "Bloemendaal", "Restaurant", null, new { @class = "btn btn-addOtherEvent" })

    </article>   
</div>
<div class="homeArticles">
    <article class="articlehome">

        <h3 class="homeart"> Specials </h3>
        <img width="182" height="268" src="~/Content/Images/Home1.png" id="winkelmandjeimg" />
        <p class="articletekst">
            Although IHFF's name suggests it's all about film, IHFF have expanded their revenue to discussions, lectures and even theaterical exhibits. 
            All these events are summarized in our Special page, organized by day. Make sure to take a look at the specials, they are all free of costs although there is a 
            mandatory capacity whom can't be exceeded. 
        </p>
        @Html.ActionLink("Show me specials!", "Wednesday", "Special", null, new { @class = "btn btn-addOtherEvent" })

    </article>
    <article class="articlehome">

        <h3 class="homeart"> Culture </h3>
        <img width="182" height="268" src="~/Content/Images/nieuwe-bavo1-klein.jpeg" id="winkelmandjeimg" />
        <p class="articletekst">
            The city of haarlem provides numerous cultural experiences. The IHFF does not only support the movie and theater loving visitors.
            it also supports the wide variety of cultural monuments and places in Haarlem. 
            Make sure to take a look at the astonishing cultural experiences, all shown on our 'Culture' page.
        </p>
        @Html.ActionLink("Show me culture!", "Monument", "Culture", null, new { @class = "btn btn-addOtherEvent" })

    </article>
</div>















